spec_data.Name: perl-Module-Extract-VERSION
spec_data.Description:
This module lets you pull out of module source code the version number for the
module. It assumes that there is only one $VERSION in the file.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Fri 28 Jul 2017 01:22:13 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Extract a module version without running code
